nodes.text: The P-s5.6 twin ion engine was an ion drive manufactured by Sienar Fleet Systems during the height of the Galactic Civil War. It was an upgraded version of the SFS P-s4 twin ion engine used aboard TIE/LN starfighters.
The SFS P-s5.6 model was fitted aboard the TIE/IN interceptors of the Galactic Empire, making them among the fastest starfighters in the galaxy. These engines were rated at 175 KTU.
